Actalent (T4) Employee Benefits

    Vacation – 4% accrual of your hours worked per week (comes out to two weeks per year, you’re also free to take additional unpaid time off)
    Overtime pay after 44/hours worked
    Ontario stat holidays are covered based on a 4-week average of working hours (if you work full-time, you’re paid out for the full day)
